高等高分子化學                           ADVANCED POLYMER CHEMISTRY


  	高等高分子化學This course will focus mainly on the principles of various polymerizations, including reaction types, reaction kinetics, molecular weight control, and industrial applications. The course contents will comprise four main categories: step polymerization (polycondensation), free radical polymerization, chain copolymerization, and emulsion polymerization and its manufacturing processes. The curriculum will emphasize on reaction mechanism, reaction kinetics, molecular weight control, and microstructure control of different polymerizations, followed with their industrial applications. 1) Introduction 2) Step polymerization (polycondensation): Types of step polymerization, polymerization kinetics, and methods of molecular weight control. 3) Free radical polymerization: Mechanism of radical polymerization, polymerization kinetics, molecular weight control, microstructures, and industrial manufacturing processes. 4) Chain copolymerization: Polymerization kinetics of chain copolymerization and microstructure control. 5) Emulsion polymerization: Mechanism of emulsion polymerization, polymerization kinetics, molecular weight control, and industrial polymerization processes.

課程教育目標 

A 厚植專業知識與應用能力 Enhance professional knowledge and application skill/abilityB 強化獨立思考及創新研發能力 Strengthen independent thinking and innovative research and development 
課程基本素養與核心能力 

A 專精之化工知識及開發前瞻技術之能力。

B 獨立思考、規劃與執行研究計畫、撰寫研究報告及口頭發表之能力。

C 結合理論知識與實務操作以解決工程問題之能力。

D 結合化工專業知識與跨領域技術以發展新興科技之能力。

H 終身學習成長之能力。


